{{zh-forms|[[和尚]][[打]][[伞]]，[[无法无天]]|[[和尚打傘，無法無天]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: héshàng dǎ sǎn, wúfǎwútiān
===Etymology===
Literally: (like a bald) monk holding up an umbrella - no (respect for) law<sup>1</sup> and order<sup>2</sup>.<br>
<sup>1</sup>law [[法纪|法(纪)]] and hair [[头发|(头)发]] are [[homophone]]s in Chinese.<br>
<sup>2</sup>[[天]] literally means sky, but it is also short for [[天理]] (heavenly justice).

===Idiom ([[歇后语]])===
# no respect for law and order; unruly

